  "formulaSource": "Equipment base pricing from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 national average surveys for ductless mini-split systems. SEER2 efficiency tier multipliers derived from AHRI (Air-Conditioning, Heating, and Refrigeration Institute) certified performance data. Labor rates calculated at 40% of equipment cost, adjusted for line set complexity and regional wage differences from Bureau of Labor Statistics Occupational Employment and Wage Statistics for HVAC installers (SOC 49-9021). Electrical work pricing from HomeAdvisor and licensed electrician rate surveys. Regional labor multipliers derived from BLS OES regional wage data.",
